Content:: The Course de la Paix U23 – Grand Prix Jeseníky is a stage road cycling race held annually in the Czech Republic. It is part of the UCI Europe Tour in category 2.ncup,[1] meaning it is part of the UCI Under 23 Nations' Cup. It had a rating of 2.2U from 2013 to 2014, and was upgraded to 2.ncup in 2015.
